      "patch": "@@ -2,16 +2,24 @@ This is a [Next.js](https://nextjs.org) project bootstrapped with [`create-next-\n \n ## Getting Started\n \n-First, run the development server:\n+Install deps with Bun, then run the development server:\n \n ```bash\n-npm run dev\n-# or\n-yarn dev\n-# or\n-pnpm dev\n-# or\n-bun dev\n+bun install\n+bun run dev\n+```\n+\n+Common scripts\n+\n+```bash\n+# lint\n+bun run lint\n+\n+# production build\n+bun run build\n+\n+# start the built app locally\n+bun run start\n ```\n \n Open [http://localhost:3000](http://localhost:3000) with your browser to see the result."
